{"tid":1423302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[學術討論］市民可否要求市民出示身分證？","createTime":"2019-08-06T13:28:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T13:57:51.000Z","uid":63822,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2edcfdf148047b049a3cece31af8dd4ed5177b8c","tid":1423302,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:28:24.000Z","msg":"劇本如下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=市民A <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=市民B<br />\nA：先生，過黎，身分證。<br />\nB：委任證呢？我點知你係唔係警察。<br />\nA：我唔需要比你睇證件，麻煩你合作呀。拎個袋黎睇睇。唔好玩野呀，小心我告鳩你！<br />\n<br />\n算唔算冒警？<br />\n<br />\n好怕有人冒警見藍絲就撚令香港警察形象再下跌。（雖然都冇得再跌）"},{"pid":"92c2646f9d784154cca9c60966f7e8bc32e6b048","tid":1423302,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:31:56.000Z","msg":"求解答"},{"pid":"ff8d418cd78b79f7acafb716c1e0c7533397167a","tid":1423302,"uid":294614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:32:56.000Z","msg":"（突發）（多圖） 炮台山勁多狗同狗車<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1422223\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1422223</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1a6eb0fb9704074cb76c4dd09e98d6207dbf2408","tid":1423302,"uid":29093,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:32:57.000Z","msg":"B：委任證呢？<span style=\"color: red;\">我點知你係唔係警察</span>。<br />\nA：<span style=\"color: red;\">我唔需要比你睇證件，麻煩你合作呀</span>。<br />\n<br />\n我估法律上,  A 係有問題<br />\n因為 B 係有合理懷疑 A 係咪警察<br />\n但 A 就清楚回應 「唔需要比你睇證件，麻煩你合作。」<br />\n有冒警既企圖 <br />\n<br />\n所以依個唔係市民查市民既問題 , A 答得柒暴露左個企圖"},{"pid":"0df661fa7d55f90bc7295d060f44464b74b9d1ed","tid":1423302,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:33:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">搶野呀！</span></span>"},{"pid":"1a31f08c434c30fdcccd646142e7518b138b812e","tid":1423302,"uid":54511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a6eb0fb9704074cb7